{"tid":388300,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上朋友屋企,哇佢老母真係好煩!","createTime":"2017-09-05T11:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T04:18:30.000Z","uid":119688,"like":46,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"816a6c9c2df72468f682abc5c992644d54faca8d","tid":388300,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"唔怪得我朋友日日都咁灰 睇開哂<br />\n一上去禮貌上叫聲伯母<br />\n我都未開口 佢老母就開口罵我朋友<br />\n話做咩點點點 又點點點 但唔係朋友有做錯野<br />\n總知就係好煩果類老母 係唔係都屌左先<br />\n都入房關埋度門 我同朋友講你老母真係極品<br />\n之後佢喊左出黎 我一野攬住佢<br />\n點知有反應 扯扯地旗<br />\n直接禁低左個朋友埋牙..."},{"pid":"0b9ccedc9aadf61ee34e29d69197e0b9e48243c2","tid":388300,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"推 不能只有我看到"},{"pid":"6ae1cb9e2818bf459cf567ff1b3de6a810a8c8ba","tid":388300,"uid":4402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"最後有冇互射返次先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91331b1f5cb212320d948b004c43054cc886791b","tid":388300,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推 不能只有我看到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e9feb58556b53995bc1474427868994e8fa687","tid":388300,"uid":3454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"椰汁炸豬扒 椰汁炸豬扒"},{"pid":"c04870ce83fcda4e7f0e007c4c217884078c5d9a","tid":388300,"uid":94090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"我浪費咗人生既三十秒睇咗篇咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c341deea6629b5cb6f4a45e079506a9c736908","tid":388300,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"皮已正，請繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b